Private Loan Contracts Between Individuals
Create a simple written record for a loan between friends — no BankID, no legal machinery, no identity verification.
The value is clarity and memory, not legal enforceability.

V1 candidate — simple enough to ship alongside or just after the MVP core.
Priority: after Phase 2 basics, before Phase 3 debt tracking.

Lender flow:
Define amount, optional interest, repayment date or schedule
Add borrower by name or email
App generates a plain-language PDF or shareable summary link
Borrower clicks link to acknowledge — no account required from them

Payment Tracking
Mark repayments manually as they happen.
Running balance visible to lender.
Optional reminder notifications at due dates.

Dedicated Loan Account
Each loan acts like its own account — balance, payment log, schedule.
Fully transparent record for the lender.

What this is: a shared record both parties have seen and acknowledged.
What this is not: legally binding, a bank product, or a regulated financial instrument.

Auth: existing session for lender. Borrower needs no account. BankID not required — not now, not later for this feature.
